en_262659_0	A special memorial to commemorate the memories of fallen War Heroes in the 2nd World War built by Ex-servicemen and those still living in their dotage was unveiled at Galkoriya area in Polonnaruwa on Saturday (3) by HE the President Maithripala Sirisena.
en_262659_1	Floral tributes were paid to the memorial by the day’s Chief Guest, retired veterans and family members of all fallen War Heroes on the occasion.
en_262659_2	It was followed by religious observances, meant to transfer merits on the departed ones.
en_262659_3	(Picture Courtesy – President Media)
